address2: 7th Floor, Office No. 7010 C & D Viman Nagar
longBusinessSummary: Quick Heal Technologies Limited engages in the provision of security software products and solutions to consumers, small businesses, government establishments, and corporate houses in India and internationally. The company operates through Retail, Enterprise and Government, and Mobile segments. It offers antivirus solutions for PCs, laptops, mac, and windows. Its products portfolio includes GoDeep.AI, a malware hunting engine; and Seqrite Hawk, a cybersecurity solution. The company also offers HawkkEye, a central security management solution; HawkHuntXDR, an extended detection and response solution; HawkkScan, a data privacy management solution; HawkkProtect, a zero trust user access solution; MSSP portal, a managed secured service platform; endpoint security (EPS); endpoint security cloud(EPS cloud); and EMM-m suite & workspace, enterprise mobility management solution. In addition, the company offers technical and after-sales support services. It sells its products through a network of service providers, system integrators, resellers, and distributors. The company offers its products under Seqrite brand. Quick Heal Technologies Limited was incorporated in 1995 and is based in Pune, India.
